		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You breathe a twisting white gas which cripples enemies.</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 20 ft. cone - 1/Long Rest - Magical</p><p><strong>[[/save con]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 2d6 poison]] damage*, and the target is &amp;reference[poisoned] for 1 minute. Target rolls again at end of their turns, ending effect on success.</p><p>If a creature is reduced to 0 hit points with this breath weapon, the creature falls &amp;reference[Unconscious], does not roll death saving throws or die as a result of this damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> This ability's damage increases by 2d6 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 4d6 poison]]{4d6}), 11th level ([[/damage 6d6 poison]]{6d6}), and 17th level ([[/damage 8d6 poison]]{8d6}).</p>",
